## 5 Conclusion  

5 ConclusionIn this paper, we propose a novel red- teaming approach AGENTPOISON to holistically assess the safety and trustworthiness of RAG- based LLM agents. Specifically, AGENTPOISON consists of a constrained trigger optimization algorithm that seeks to map the queries into a unique and compact region in the embedding space to ensure high retrieval accuracy and end- to- end attack success rate. Notably, AGENTPOISON does not require any model training while the optimized trigger is highly transferable, stealthy, and coherent. Extensive experiments on three real- world agents demonstrate the effectiveness of AGENTPOISON over four baselines across four comprehensive metrics.  

